#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.12:0.2"
msgid "2. Aniccavagga"
msgstr "2. Impermanence"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Aniccasutta"
msgstr "12. Impermanence"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.12:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "sn22.12:1.2"
msgid "sāvatthiyaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn22.12:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.12:1.4"
msgid ""
"“rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ, vedanā aniccā, saññā aniccā, saṅkhārā aniccā, "
"viññāṇaṃ aniccaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness are "
"impermanent."

msgctxt "sn22.12:1.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpasmimpi nibbindati, vedanāyapi "
"nibbindati, saññāyapi nibbindati, saṅkhāresupi nibbindati, viññāṇasmimpi "
"nibbindati."
msgstr ""
"Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with form, "
"feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness."

msgctxt "sn22.12:1.6"
msgid ""
"Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re "
"freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed."

msgctxt "sn22.12:1.7"
msgid ""
"‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānātī”ti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been "
"completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any "
"state of existence.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.12:1.8"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
